Chris Koch [[Image: |250px|center]] General Information Gender Male Birthplace Melrose, Massachusetts Years Active 1993–present

Christopher "Chris" Koch is an American film and television director. He has directed episodes of My Name Is Earl and Scrubs and also directed the film Snow Day.
